```plantuml
@startuml TestHaters_ctflow

actor User

participant "VS Code Extension" as Extension
participant "React Webview UI" as Webview
participant "Cypress" as Cypress
participant "Firebase" as Firebase

== User Interaction ==
User -> Webview : Open visual editor
Webview -> Extension : Request initial data
Extension -> Webview : Provide initial data

== Drag-and-Drop Test Creation ==
User -> Webview : Drag and drop nodes
Webview -> Webview : Update visual graph
Webview -> Firebase : Sync changes (optional)

== Compilation of Test Flow ==
User -> Webview : Click "Compile to Cypress"
Webview -> Extension : Request compilation
Extension -> Webview : Compile visual graph
Webview -> Webview : Generate Cypress code
Webview -> Extension : Send generated Cypress code

== Test Execution ==
User -> Extension : Execute test
Extension -> Cypress : Run test code
Cypress -> Extension : Return test results
Extension -> User : Display test results

@enduml
```